  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  healthy subjects

          -  50-80 years old

          -  moderate to heavy weight (BMI 25-30)

          -  must be able to change diet/take supplements at home

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  diabetes

          -  younger than 50 years

          -  BMI &lt; 25

          -  psychiatric medication

          -  severe disease

          -  MMSE &lt; 26

          -  eating disorders
      </textblock>
